column5: Hey guys, just wanted to share a pic of my first steelhead of the year!
Nice, was that fish caught on Saturday?  Tony
Tony, yup that was caught on Saturday.
Thanks, there wasn't a lot of people that day cause the water was a little high and dark but we fished it anyway. A couple of other people caught some steelies that day too.
Nice spawned out female steelhead you caught there,its great to see so many pics of all these steelhead that have layed their precious cargo of eggs....well done thanks for sharing   cheers
Thanks guys. Hope to catch some more this weekend!
Funny I know exactly what creek you were fishing and the day...  Tony
